               We need not ſearch farre for examples: behold the great honour the world here gaue to Chriſt, and we ſhall ſee the fallacie 
                     •
                  hereof, which S. Bernard well obſerued,S. Bernard hādling this place, Quis ſperare debeat in in
                     
                        •
                     erto gloriae temporalis, &amp;c. Who would now 
