                  he will forgiue my manifolde ſinnes: for mercy and wrath come from him, and his indignation commeth downe vpon ſinners. This dangerous ſicknes, I will labour (God willing) in what I purpoſe to ſpeake more vpon this texte, to cure: for I am verily perſwaded, that the number is almoſt infinite, of them that being deluded with this deceitfull hope, doe ruſh headlong into eternall torments; Neither is there any Inginne of that olde cankered Serpent more frequent, or more to be feared.
